        "Title": "Operation: Absolute Silence",
        "Location": "LOCATION_COASTALTOWN_NIGHT",
        "PublicId": "104653429000",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/CoastalTown/_scene_mamba.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 4028354c-4c79-4b13-89e6-5c8763408fc9).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening, 47.\n\nYour targets are five individuals currently gathered within a landslide-stricken area, now repurposed into a public space filled with music and unaware civilians.\n\nAmidst the melancholic atmosphere, you will eliminate all five targets.\nFour of them must be taken down using a sniper rifle. The method for the final target is left to your discretion.\n\nDespite the crowd, this operation demands absolute precision.\nNo bodies must be found. No suspicion must be raised.\n\nRemember, 47 —\nthis mission does not end with the final shot.\nYou are not safe until you leave the area.\n\nGood luck.",
        "GameVersion": "8.23.0.86",
